channel.description:
First find this in Commands.java
[code]import com.rs.game.player.content.dungeoneering.DungeonPartyManager;[/code]

Under that add this:
[code]import com.rs.game.player.content.Magic;[/code]


Now add this under any command:
[code]			if (cmd[0].equalsIgnoreCase("mine")) {
				Magic.sendNormalTeleportSpell(player, 0, 0, new WorldTile(X Coordinate,
						Y Coordinate, 0));					
				player.getPackets().sendGameMessage(
					"You have teleported to ENTER PLACE HERE.");
                                }[/code]

* Replace the [b]X Coordinate[/b], [b]Y Coordinate[/b], and the [b]ENTER PLACE HERE[/b] with your information!
